data.description: Welcome to your dream home in desirable Fort Collins, Colorado! Built in 2013, this spacious 3 bed, 3 bathroom house is sure to impress. The stunning stainless steel appliances in the kitchen are a chef's dream, making cooking and entertaining a breeze. Cozy up on chilly evenings in front of the warm gas fireplace in the inviting living room or around the backyard firepit. The bedrooms are spacious and perfect for relaxation and restful sleep. This home is located in a sought-after area, offering peace and quiet while still being close to all the amenities that Fort Collins has to offer. Don't miss your chance to make this stunning home your own!
